          "title": "About the Course",
          "entries": [
            {
              "title": "About the Course",
              "content": "Read about Canadian history from 1800-1900 through biographies, primary source documents, history spines, and historical fiction. View images and reference atlases and maps to set the people and events in their time and place. Update History Charts and Book of Centuries.\n\nThis topic is included in the following course(s): History: Grades 11-12 (Canada)"
            }
          ]
        },
